---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Sponsor a Child in India — Support Orphans | GHI"
  description="Sponsor a child in India through Global Hope India's Christian ministry. $50/month provides food, education, and the love of Christ to orphans. Give today."
  ogImage="https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-img_4700-scaled.jpg"
  keywords="sponsor child India Christian, support orphans in India, building orphanages in India, donate to India missions, orphan care India, transforming lives in India"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "DonateAction",
      "name": "Sponsor a Child in India",
      "description": "Sponsor a child in India through Christian ministry. Your gift provides food, education, and the love of Christ to orphans.",
      "recipient": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Global Hope India", "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org" },
      "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org/give/orphan-care"
    })}></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1D1C1C]" style="background-image:url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-img_4700-scaled.jpg');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-12 pt-40">
      <p class="text-[#1d803f] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Orphan Care</p>
      <h1 style="color:white!important;" class="max-w-3xl font-bold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.2]">Sponsor a Child<br/>in India</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg max-w-xl">India is home to half the world's orphans. Your gift provides food, shelter, education, and the love of Christ.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT STATS -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] py-10 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center text-white">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">$50</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">1 month of orphan care</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">599</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Orphans sponsored</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">100K</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Hygiene kits delivered</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">25+</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Years serving children</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Sponsor an Orphan in India?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
            <p>India is home to <strong>more than 30 million orphans</strong> — nearly half the world's orphan population. Many of these children live on the streets, lack access to education, and have never experienced the love of a family.</p>
            <p>When you sponsor a child in India through a Christian ministry, you do more than provide food and shelter. You give a child <strong>access to education, healthcare, and the transformative love of Jesus Christ</strong>. Our orphan care partners operate homes and schools where children grow up in a nurturing, faith-filled environment.</p>
            <p>Global Hope India partners with organizations like <strong>Raja's Home</strong> in Hyderabad, which cares for children with special needs, and <strong>Elim School</strong> in Manipur, where Pastor Mayon provides quality education alongside spiritual discipleship.</p>
            <p>For just <strong>$50 per month</strong>, you can sponsor a child's care — covering meals, education, clothing, and a safe home. Your generosity is building orphanages and transforming lives in India, one child at a time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="bg-[#F8F5EF] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-xl font-bold mb-4">Support Orphan Care in India</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555] text-sm mb-6">Your donation provides food, education, and the love of Christ to orphaned and vulnerable children across India.</p>
            <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-[#06038D] hover:bg-[#1D1C1C] text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md w-full">Donate Now</a>
            <p class="text-[#666] text-xs mt-4 font-medium">Over 85% of every dollar goes directly to programs in India.</p>
            <p class="text-[#999] text-xs mt-1">Global Hope India is a 501(c)(3). All gifts are tax-deductible.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-4">
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/767b76c41ccc43b3c07f07c94435a4dcc3ad13b3-500x500.svg" alt="GuideStar Platinum Seal" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/07b08d8f4d9321bb85fa7814ef0d65a742b3463e-500x500.png" alt="Charity Navigator 100" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/f256d3af6f9dbfbc282103b8fb3f7037a98d64db-500x500.png" alt="Better Business Bureau" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Your Gift at Work</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555]">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#1d803f] font-bold">$50</span> — 1 month of care for a child</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#1d803f] font-bold">$150</span> — 3 months of care for a child</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#1d803f] font-bold">$300</span> — 6 months of care for a child</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#1d803f] font-bold">$600</span> — Full year of care for a child</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] text-center py-12 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-[26px] md:text-[36px] mb-4">Transform a Child's Life Today</h2>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Every child deserves hope. Sponsor an orphan in India and provide the care, education, and love that transforms lives for eternity.</p>
      <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-stone-100 text-[#1d803f] font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">Sponsor a Child</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
